==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Underdose
<hw>Un"der*dose`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A dose which is
less than required; a small or insufficient dose.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Underdose</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Underdose
<hw>Un`der*dose"</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t. & i.</pos> <def>To give
an underdose or underdoses to; to practice giving insufficient
doses.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Underdrain</ent>⟦br⟧
